Title: [ENDED]GBX-The Crypto Harbour.Gibraltar-based Crypto Exchange&Token Platform
Body: You will get 24hrs early access if you have $1000 worth of RKT in your GBX account at that specific moment in time (before the early access opening) and you no longer have to do KYC on any ICOs if you have already KYCd with us. Every single token sale will have its price peg and cutoff time for having the necessary token balance. At that moment, if you have at least that minimum balance, then you will qualify for the Early Access. This will be announced within each token sale's details It should only be open for RKT holders. --- The Early Access Sale is available to GBX account holders with GBX account balances of at least 1000 USD worth of Rock Token (RKT) before the sale, at 11:00:00 SGT (03:00:00 UTC) on 4th April. Due to time constraints for new account holders who may not be able to obtain RKT in time, for this specific T2T sale, we are also allowing account holders who prefund their accounts with at least 1000 USD worth of ETH to qualify for the Early Access Sale. For account holders who use RKT to participate in the sale, they will be using the RKT to T2T rate. For account holders with only ETH, the ETH to T2T rate will be used instead. GBX undertakes to convert the received ETH in the Early Access Sale from such accounts to RKT for Traceto. --- The platform will be launched in April. --- The GBX aims to be the world’s leading token sale and cryptocurrency exchange which is licensed under a specifically created regime for DLT businesses. It also intends to be the first platform and exchange of its kind run by and according to the principles of a regulated stock exchange. It is also the only platform of its kind to form part of a much larger fintech ecosystem and financing pathway plan.

Body: Please, note, that withdrawal takes time, so don`t worry if you do not get your tokens to the wallet more than several hours. (Pending doesn't mean it has been sent on the Blockchain. It means it is still pending our approval to send it, as we are holding tokens in cold storage. We will come up with the list of definitions and withdrawals processes later today.)

Author: hufflepuff4life
Title: [ENDED]GBX-The Crypto Harbour.Gibraltar-based Crypto Exchange&Token Platform
Body: Token Withdrawal Process at GBX  Withdrawal refers to the action of transferring the tokens from GBX to the user's personal wallet. We take great precautions in making sure withdrawals are done safely and securely. We have implemented a 2 factor authentication mechanism via the user’s registered email through out the process.  First, the user needs to authenticate his or her wallet address for the withdrawal.  Second, after the wallet has been authenticated and the user has initiated the withdrawal process, an email confirmation will be sent to the user's email. The status at this time on the GBX platform will be "pending email confirmation". Once the user confirms the withdrawal by clicking the link in the email, the status is will be changed to "pending" on the platform.  All "pending" withdrawals will be put up for processing at 8AM UTC daily (weekends excluded) unless otherwise notified. Their status will change from "pending" to "processing". Should there be any holiday that renders the service unavailable, all customers will be notified beforehand.  The process of moving crypto from our cold storage to external addresses can take up to a few hours as it includes a few manual steps and needs multiple signatures.  GBX does not take any fee for crypto deposits and crypto withdrawals.

In order for the upgrade and distribution process to go smoothly concurrently, the GBX Platform will be put under maintenance during the upgrade. When you log back into your GBX account on March 12th, not only will you see your RKT balance, you will also find a brand new interface. We are certain that you will like the new look and experience!  Rock On and stay tuned for more updates throughout the month!  GBX Team

Author: Madlen
Title: [ENDED]GBX-The Crypto Harbour.Gibraltar-based Crypto Exchange&Token Platform
Body: GBX aims to become the world's first licensed and regulated platform for the sale of tokens and digital exchange assets managed by the regulated European Union stock exchange  More specifically, gbx-this is expected to be:  a global marketplace for listing and selling tokens that satisfy the strict due diligence process and the admissibility process set out in the "GBX rules"; exchange of high-quality digital assets, including a market in which issuers of tokens, traders and investors can confidently and reliably participate in a platform where the listed tokens have been subjected to an institution-level approval process.

Author: satosha9962
Title: [ENDED]GBX-The Crypto Harbour.Gibraltar-based Crypto Exchange&Token Platform
Body: Gibraltar is known as a major financial centre. Once again, this small British Overseas territory, lives up its name.  Gibraltar leads the way in setting up a world-leading token sale platform and cryptocurrency exchange.  "The Gibraltar Blockchain Exchange (GBX) aims to be a world-leading institutional-grade token sale platform and cryptocurrency exchange. Built upon principles of decentralisation and community consensus, we seek to create a new era of trust, openness and global acceptance for the crypto industry, one quality token listing at a time."  "With a wealth of capital markets experience at its helm, and years of understanding from a process-driven traditional stock exchange, the GBX has the potential to redefine perceptions and develop new industry standards. A new age for Token Listing is coming."  "The Crypto Harbour Building a World-Leading Token Sale Platform & Cryptocurrency Exchange The GBX intends to facilitate token sales similar to existing platforms but from a governed position. The GBX aims to put in place best practices, innovative sponsor staking regime and diligent whitelisting procedures. Coupled with a token marketplace that would consist of only of high quality listings and an equally esteemed, AML/KYC cleared investor pool. In addition, advisory, corporate, banking and payment services are part of the integrated offerings GBX could provide.  The GBX would also provide a top-tier centralised cryptocurrency exchange for high volume, liquidity and quality cryptocurrencies. Under construction with institutional grade technology, multi-sig security, 100% auditable reserves, insurance protection and fiat onboarding capabilities, the future of cryptocurrency trading could begin with the GBX."   "The GBX is a subsidiary of the Gibraltar Stock Exchange The GBX intends to apply for a DLT Provider’s license from the GFSC. The GSX is regulated by GFSC under License number FSC 1231B and operates as an EU-regulated market, recognised by ESMA (European Regulator) and HMRC (UK)."   GBX website: https://gbx.gi/  Watch the GBX CREO, Nick Cowan explain the concept on Bloomberg: https://youtu.be/A83S2uFiWPQ  Some news. https://news.bitcoin.com/gibraltar-launches-regulation-to-protect-value-and-reputation/

Author: piggyfrog
Title: [ENDED]GBX-The Crypto Harbour.Gibraltar-based Crypto Exchange&Token Platform
Body: The GBX aims to be the world’s first licensed and regulated token sale platform and digital asset exchange, operated by the European Union regulated stock exchange.  Using a sponsor and rules-based system, the GBX will apply to be licensed by the Gibraltar Financial Services Commission (“GFSC”) under the Financial Services (Distributed Ledger Technology Providers) Regulations 2017 (“DLT Regulations”), which came into operation on 1 January 2018 in Gibraltar.  More specifically, GBX is expected to be: (a) a global listing and token sales springboard for utility tokens that have satisfied a strict due diligence process and admission process set out in the “GBX Rules”; and  (b) a high-quality digital asset exchange, including a marketplace where issuers of utility tokens, traders and investors can participate with confidence and trust in a platform where the tokens listed have been subjected to an institutional grade approval process. Check out the advantages part of our homepage here https://gbx.gi/#advantage We are based in Gibraltar, which has a very token friendly community and actually endorses [Suspicious link removed]panies, literally the perfect jurisdiction for us.

Author: jscholz
Title: [ENDED]GBX-The Crypto Harbour.Gibraltar-based Crypto Exchange&Token Platform
Body: Hi team,  While waiting for the details to appear on Telegram I'd like to remind everyone of what GBX is all about:  The Gibraltar Blockchain Exchange (GBX) intends to build a world leading token sale platform and digital asset exchange. GBX is a subsidiary of the EU-regulated Gibraltar Stock Exchange (GSX).  Launching in 2018, GBX vision encompasses:  (a)    a token sale / ICO platform for utility tokens that satisfy admission rules and a strict due diligence process; (b)    a high-quality digital asset exchange, listing tokens that meet an institutional grade approval process, and (c)     a fully tokenised stock exchange providing a path from initial token sale to funding via traditional bond markets or equity issuances.  The GBX team completed its global roadshow, sharing the message of both its Exchange, and the work of Gibraltar as one of the first jurisdictions to support the new crypto-economy.  At the beginning of January 2018, the Gibraltar Financial Services Commission (GFSC) introduced a new license regime, and is now one of the first jurisdictions in the world to provide regulatory certainty for companies utilizing Distributed Ledger Technology (DLT). DLT Regulations (GFSC).  The GBX will apply for a DLT Provider’s license from the GFSC.  The GBX team is also excited to introduce plans for the RockToken (RKT) serving its ecosystem in three primary ways:  1.  Signal community membership and shared buy-in in the overall vision 2.  Deliver a premium experience for certain users and traders corresponding to their comfort with the industry 3.  Incentivize and reward community members for upholding GBX values of transparency  Please watch out for further news on GBX and the RockToken. More announcements for the token generation event coming soon in early 2018.   Website: https://gbx.gi Telegram: https://t.me/GBXCommunity Bitcointalk: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2684176.0 Medium blog: https://medium.com/@Gibraltar.Blockchain.Exchange LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/company/18286558/ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/GibBlockEx/ Twitter: https://twitter.com/GibBlockEx Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/GBXCommunity/
